2011-12-02 Gary Funck <gary@intrepid.com>

	Preliminary split of UPC Specification into language
	and library parts.
	* Makefile: New.  Makefile to build the UPC core library
	specification.
	* upc-lib-core-spec.tar.gz: New.  Tar file with both LaTeX
	and generated PDF files.
	* upc-lib-core-spec.tex: New.  The UPC core library
	specification driver file.
	* upc-lib-core.tex: New.  The main description of the
	UPC core library.
